Summary:        Accounting and aggregation toolsuite for IPv4 and IPv6
License:        GPL-2.0-only
Group:          Productivity/Networking/Diagnostic
URL:            http://www.pmacct.net/
Source:         http://www.pmacct.net/pmacct-%{version}.tar.gz
